Vendors & Suppliers


Welcome to The Kroger Co.’s Business 2 Business Vendor Site. The Kroger Co. is one of the nation’s top grocery retailers. Our mission is to be a leader in the distribution and merchandising of food, pharmacy, health and personal care items, seasonal merchandise, and related products and services. We place considerable importance on forging strong supplier partnerships. Our suppliers, large or small, local or global, are essential components in accomplishing our mission. We look forward to working with you. For more information on becoming a supplier, please click here.







